RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: PRODUCT_CODE IN (SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A,OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR C,OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = C.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE= C.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.PRODUCT_CODE= C.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.BRANCH = C.BRANCH_CODE AND S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO, A.USER_REF_NO, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.COUNTERPARTY, A.BRANCH, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1, C.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B, OLTMS_PRODUCT C, LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST_MASTER D WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY AND C.PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = D.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A','Y') AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND D.SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN = 'Y' AND D.RATE_FIXING_REQD = 'Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SMVWS_USER_BRANCHES B WHERE B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND B.BRANCH_CODE = sypks_utils.get_branch(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO))
